General.Name: Etiler İnci Bufe Gida Sanayi ve Dis Ticaret AS
General.Description: Etiler Gida Ve Ticari Yatirimlar Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi operates fast-food spots. The company offers doners, versions, portions, snacks, burgers, toasts, cold and hot sandwiches, breakfast, cold drinks, freshly squeezed fruit juices, desserts, and salads. It operates a network of 43 branches in 10 provinces of Turkey. The company was founded in 1964 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.
